{"data":{"article":{"html":"<p>When using Ferdi 5.4.0 or greater, you can choose to use Ferdi without an account. In this case, Ferdi will internally create a local server that allows it to save all settings on your local machine.</p>\n<p>To use Ferdi without an account, select \"Use Ferdi without an account\" on the splash screen, login welcome screen, register or login screens:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/enAr7Rg.png\" width=\"40%\"></img>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lltAl98.png\" width=\"40%\"></img>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VV73ExC.png\" width=\"40%\"></img>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uUKDazi.png\" width=\"40%\"></img></p>\n<h2>Import your existing account</h2>\n<p>View <a href=\"./transfer\">our guide on how to transfer your account data</a>.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"without-account/howto","title":"How do I use Ferdi without an account?"}},"footer":{"html":"<div \n  align=\"center\" \n  style=\"display:flex; justify-content: center;align-items:center;flex-direction:column;margin-top:2.5rem;\">\n  <h4>Still have questions?</h4>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/getferdi/ferdi/issues\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"feather feather-github\"><path d=\"M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22\"></path></svg>\n    <span style=\"margin-left: 0.2rem;\">Create a new issue on GitHub</span>\n  </a>\n</div>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"article":"without-account/howto"}}